500
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:49,520
It's barely edible.

501
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,720
You'll get used to it.

502
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:00,360
All right.

503
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:02,040
Go home.

504
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:03,080
I'm leaving.

505
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:05,360
Ruoxin, are you really okay?

506
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:08,880
