530
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,480
I'm leaving too.

531
00:31:56,560 --> 00:31:58,880
Su Yang found a house.
I'm moving tomorrow.

532
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,160
Wait.

533
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,880
Su Yang?

534
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:03,320
