544
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:23,040
It's quite nice.

545
00:32:23,120 --> 00:32:25,040
It's 5,000 yuan a month?

546
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:26,720
That's expensive.

547
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:29,320
